<div class="indent"><strong><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Franchise/Superman" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Franchise/Superman">Superman</a></strong>: Have you ever heard of Mr. Mxyzptlk? <br><strong><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Franchise/GreenLantern" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Franchise/GreenLantern">Green Lantern</a></strong>: No. <br><strong>Superman</strong>: No! That's right. It's because I do my damn job.
