<div class="indent"><strong>Merlin</strong>: Don't make me mad. <br><strong>Space pirate</strong>: I'm on the verge of taking over all the territory of all the pirates Arthur's put out of business. I don't think one old man&mdash; <br><strong>Merlin</strong>: Have you heard of the dual dragons of Dinas Emrys? <br><strong>Space pirate</strong>: No. <br><strong>Merlin</strong>: <em>They</em> made me mad.
