</li><li> <em>Life of Wily</em>, an early <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/MegaManClassic" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/MegaManClassic">Mega Man (Classic)</a></em> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/SpriteComic" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/SpriteComic">sprite comic</a>, features <a class="urllink" href="http://low.newbsoft.com/index.php?date=2001-08-10">a unique delivery on the idea<img src="https://static.tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/external_link.gif" height="12" width="12" style="border:none;"></a>:
