<div class="indent">"For those of you who are young and have no idea who Pauly Shore is... <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/YouDoNotWantToKnow" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/YouDoNotWantToKnow">good</a></em>.
</div></li><li> And <em>again</em> for his review of <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Anime/LittleNemoAdventuresInSlumberland" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Anime/LittleNemoAdventuresInSlumberland">Little Nemo: Adventures in Slumberland</a></em>:
<div class="indent"><strong>Nostalgia Critic:</strong> Remember the movie Little Nemo: Adventures in Slumberland? (<a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BigNo" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BigNo">Buzzer</a>) Well, how about <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicStrip/LittleNemo" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicStrip/LittleNemo">the comic strip</a>? (<a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BigNo" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BigNo">Buzzer</a>) The opera? (<a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BigNo" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BigNo">Buzzer</a>) <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/LittleNemoTheDreamMaster" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/LittleNemoTheDreamMaster">The game</a>? (<a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BigNo" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BigNo">Buzzer</a>) The frickin&#146; postcards? (<a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BigNo" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BigNo">Buzzer</a>) Well, then! I guess there is no point in reviewing this! Bye!
</div><div class="indent">(Credits music plays until he's punched back into his seat)
